CHIMAERA-OVERCLOCK: Corey Remap Reference

Philosophy: Split the pad into Left-Side Traversal/Momentum, Right-Side Pure Violence, with automated wide-angle perspective camera vectors.

Layout Configuration
Primary Digital Actions
R2: Primary Fire (Continuous projectile hammering).
R1: React/Deflect (Parry/Block last-resort defense mechanism).
L2: Asset Morph (Tap: Handguns $\leftrightarrow$ Shotgun / Hold: Manual AMR Sniper).
L1: Kinetic Sprint Accelerator (Single-tap 3s burst).
Directional Triggers & Anchors
Left Stick: 360-degree vector steering.
Context Focus (Ground Hold L2): Transitions to manual sniper scope aiming reticle.
Context Focus (Air Hold L2): Initiates dead-eye time dilation until landing.
Right Stick: Pure 4-Way Hazmat Select (North, South, East, West cardinal elements).
Behavior: Fixed toggle selection state. Permanent until explicitly changed.
Face Button Core System
Circle (Air/Ground Context): Traversal Grapnel Swing. Single tap latches onto geometry anchor points.
Cross: 3-Sec Aerial Hover Jets.
Momentum Interrupt: Tapping Cross while swinging instantly breaks the Grapnel line to snap and preserve peak engine velocity.
Triangle: Contextual Heavy Payload Rocket.
Moving Stick: Ranged high-impact AoE explosive projectile.
Melee Distance: Automated Rocket Vault execution over an anomaly's face.
Neutral Stick: Straight vertical Halo 2 style kinetic self-launch rocket jump.
Square: Hazmat Grenade Deployment. Combo tool dropped to prime zones for cascading chemical reactions.
D-Pad Utility Matrix
D-Pad UP: Fast Heal / Lifeline (Short linear path matching life-bar elevation psychology).
Horizontal Axis (Left/Right): VACANT (Stripped to completely prevent panicked diagonal misclicks during high-stress encounters).
D-Pad DOWN: Contextual Action (Set-piece interactions only. Removed from active combat execution pools).
Overclock Mechanism

L3 + R3 Click: Reaper Mode. Simultaneous dual-handed stick compression.
Properties: Lasts exactly 10 seconds. Zero startup frames.
Visual/Mechanical Shift: Literal high-tech visor snaps shut. Arena desaturates into monochromatic tones while weak points and elements explode in high-contrast color. 100% of projectile damage converts to pure elemental Hazmat damage based on the active Right Stick position.


